{"tid":1644419,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[代發] 對家由幼稚園開始洗腦呀！ ！","createTime":"2019-10-10T14:15:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T14:53:43.000Z","uid":289801,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f8ff9c528b9c143c0524527e52bb0b02e70dba91","tid":1644419,"uid":289801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:15:25.000Z","msg":"琴日Twitter / Facebook 有流傳一條影片，內容係一班幼稚園生喺班房升支國國旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hLBjynMlN8Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhLBjynMlN8Q&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5dToc6H19M6%2Bti4cloj%2BWDc%3D&h=aa95c2ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hLBjynMlN8Q</a><br />\n影片中負責升旗嘅小朋友，點睇都只有4-5歲，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢地嘅動作、眼神 (尤其係扯旗果個男仔) 都無一絲猶豫，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相信都已經訓練咗一段時間<br />\n就咁睇都已經Feel陣陣強國嘅味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係幼稚園，小朋友個腦先係真正嘅白紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (中學生唔係白紙囉唔該)<br />\n呢個年紀接觸到嘅事，係絕對會影響佢確立嘅價值觀<br />\n咁早接觸「愛國教育」，無疑係洗腦式教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而呢間咁CLS嘅幼稚園係 「香港幼苗協會」嘅屬校 「聖文嘉中英幼稚園」(華貴)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一查維基，唔怪得間學校可以咁紅底<br />\n校長麥謝巧玲係民建聯南區支部副主席，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />亦係現屆華貴選區嘅區議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BA%A5%E8%AC%9D%E5%B7%A7%E7%8E%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25BA%25A5%25E8%25AC%259D%25E5%25B7%25A7%25E7%258E%25B2&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5dToc6H19M6%2Bti4cloj%2BWDc%3D&h=defe5891\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BA%A5%E8%AC%9D%E5%B7%A7%E7%8E%B2</a><br />\n<br />\n「香港幼苗協會」嘅官網入面，列出 3點辦學宗旨，其中 1 點係︰<br />\n「以正確的幼兒教育理念及措施啟發幼兒學習的興趣和潛能，為終生學習奠定基礎。」<br />\n而 麥謝巧玲 過早灌輸小朋友愛國思想，好明顯係違背呢一點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n既然校長都唔記得咗組織嘅辦學理念，我地唯有請教育局去提醒一下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家幫幫手 一人一信 send俾教育局<br />\n要求佢地交代並徹查事件，並且撤換校長，保護幼兒健全身心發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n教育局投訴電郵地址︰edbcomp@edb.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n投訴信參考︰ <br />\n有關：「聖文嘉中英文幼稚園（華貴）」校內舉行升旗禮事宜<br />\n<br />\n近日網上流出聖文嘉中英文幼稚園（華貴）」校內舉行升旗禮過程短片，短片內約4-5歲久經訓練學生純熟去展示中國式步操及升旗，本人實質疑幼稚園年紀學生根本未有能力分辨對與錯，學校卻灌輸「愛國思想」，無疑為「洗腦式教育」。現時多間學校校長表示校園不是論政的地方，但幼稚園學生已經被塗毒，莫說是什麼批判性思考。<br />\n<br />\n現就下列事項提出投訴：<br />\n1.\t該校有否得到受影響學生家長書面同意作出拍攝？<br />\n2.\t該校有否得到受影響學生家長書面同意該短片作公開用途？<br />\n3.\t該校校長麥謝巧玲同時為民建聯華貴區議員，偏頗背景實惹人擔心？<br />\n<br />\n本人要求  貴司嚴肅跟進上述事宜，為釋除家長疑慮馬上切換校長麥謝巧玲及取消「升旗禮」。望請  貴司於此函發出之日起7日內回覆跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84913d77fddccfa639b26386fab7c94b4be30d19","tid":1644419,"uid":289801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:16:16.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"9773f57a4bac1fd1012097b3c563c6e50cdacfdb","tid":1644419,"uid":289801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:16:28.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"586934289f258c50e4745df2ec3db7bbf8cad0d2","tid":1644419,"uid":289801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:16:50.000Z","msg":"自推十連 - 香港人 反抗！"},{"pid":"ad5d2432aad5b359b9117d16292f48e2ee62b106","tid":1644419,"uid":289801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:17:06.000Z","msg":"自推十連 - 段崇智 仆街！"},{"pid":"18b858d2c6546dfac61f032659f8aee676124ed4","tid":1644419,"uid":289801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:17:30.000Z","msg":"自推十連 - 暴大人 加油！"},{"pid":"3a8f326491db7d546cec63eace2d7e5af5d92a33","tid":1644419,"uid":190727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:18:11.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a4c59672453f24d6e28df2dcba227061c9ced19","tid":1644419,"uid":289801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:18:27.000Z","msg":"自推十連 - 保住 幼稚園 !"},{"pid":"c65a1e8979f96dc02a21928a56b9100a710d8268","tid":1644419,"uid":289801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:19:04.000Z","msg":"自推十連 - 唔好比政權殘害下一代！"},{"pid":"268b87405d2a0aa73fb957bfc619c13a455105ba","tid":1644419,"uid":289801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T1